==================================================
ADMIN, USAGE, SECURITY & PLATFORM OBSERVABILITY LAYER
==================================================

PURPOSE:
The platform requires an internal admin system to monitor usage, detect suspicious behavior, manage users, control costs, review system health, and understand how customers use the product.

This is required for:
- SaaS operations
- billing integrity
- AI cost control
- abuse prevention
- customer support
- product analytics
- security compliance
- GovCon trust

==================================================
ADMIN PANEL GOALS
==================================================

The admin panel should allow internal operators to:

1. View all users
2. View all companies
3. View usage by account
4. View AI token/API usage
5. View opportunity searches
6. View proposal generations
7. View exports
8. View uploaded documents
9. View billing/subscription status
10. Detect suspicious usage
11. Flag risky accounts
12. Suspend or restrict accounts
13. Review error logs
14. Review system performance
15. Understand product behavior

