==================================================
DATA COLLECTION FOR MODEL IMPROVEMENT
==================================================

Collect structured data from user behavior:

- which opportunities users ignore
- which opportunities users save
- which ones become proposals
- which ones are won/lost
- why users reject opportunities
- what gaps appear most often
- what strategies work best

IMPORTANT:
User data must be handled securely.
Do not use private company documents for model training without explicit permission.

==================================================
PRIVACY & DATA RULES
==================================================

The platform must clearly separate:

1. Platform analytics
2. Customer private data
3. Uploaded documents
4. Proposal drafts
5. Competitive intelligence records

Private user/company documents should not be exposed to other users.

Admin access to sensitive documents should be restricted and logged.

