==================================================
ROLE-BASED ADMIN ACCESS
==================================================

Admin roles:

SUPER_ADMIN:
Full access.

SUPPORT_ADMIN:
Can view users and usage, cannot view sensitive proposal docs unless granted.

BILLING_ADMIN:
Can view billing/subscription data only.

SECURITY_ADMIN:
Can view flags, audit logs, suspicious activity.

PRODUCT_ADMIN:
Can view analytics, feature usage, funnel data.

==================================================
IMPORTANT SAFETY RULES
==================================================

Admins should NOT casually access:
- private proposal drafts
- uploaded company documents
- sensitive company profiles

If sensitive data is accessed:
- log who accessed it
- log why
- log timestamp

